Item0.Text: 项目进展情况日报表(集团)

Reader.Name: tab_load
Reader.Sql: SELECT pp.projectName, cc.clientName, -- pp.busiClass, pa.guarantyOrgName, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pp.busiTypeName, pp.bankName, pp.loadBeginDate, pp.loadEndDate, pp.delayBeginDate, pp.delayEndDate, -- pp.amanName, pp.beforeAManName, pp.beforeBManName, pa.fundSource, pa.guarantyOrgName, pa.hostAreaName, pa.oprationCompanyName, pa.attributionName, pp.bmanName, pp.subBankName, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pp.loadSum, pad.dcontractCode, cc.relationMainName FROM pro_project pp LEFT JOIN pro_applyDetail pad ON pad.`apply_ID`=pp.`apply_ID` LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.`apply_ID`=pp.`apply_ID` LEFT JOIN crm_client cc ON cc.client_ID=pad.client_ID WHERE 1=1 and pp.isCreditorMark!=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and pp.reportDate ='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ORDER BY pp.loadBeginDate ASC
Reader.Description: SELECT pp.projectName, cc.clientName, -- pp.busiClass, pa.guarantyOrgName, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pp.busiTypeName, pp.bankName, pp.loadBeginDate, pp.loadEndDate, pp.delayBeginDate, pp.delayEndDate, -- pp.amanName, pp.beforeAManName, pp.beforeBManName, pa.fundSource, pa.guarantyOrgName, pa.hostAreaName, pa.oprationCompanyName, pa.attributionName, pp.bmanName, pp.subBankName, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pp.loadSum, pad.dcontractCode, cc.relationMainName FROM pro_project pp LEFT JOIN pro_applyDetail pad ON pad.`apply_ID`=pp.`apply_ID` LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.`apply_ID`=pp.`apply_ID` LEFT JOIN crm_client cc ON cc.client_ID=pad.client_ID WHERE 1=1 and pp.isCreditorMark!=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and pp.reportDate ='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ORDER BY pp.loadBeginDate ASC

Reader.Name: tab_delay
Reader.Sql: SELECT cc.clientName, pp.projectName, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pp.bankName, CASE WHEN pd.delayBeginDate IS NULL THEN pp.delayBeginDate ELSE pd.delayBeginDate END delayBeginDate, pd.delayEndDate, -- pp.amanName, -- pp.bmanName, pp.beforeAManName, pp.beforeBManName, pa.fundSource, pp.subBankName, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pd.delaySum, pa.guarantyOrgName, pa.hostAreaName, pa.oprationCompanyName, pa.attributionName, pa.`guarantyOrgName`, pad.dcontractCode, cc.relationMainName, pp.loadCode FROM pro_delay pd LEFT JOIN pro_applyDetail pad ON pad.`apply_ID`=pd.applyID LEFT JOIN pro_project pp ON pd.project_ID=pp.`project_ID` LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.`apply_ID`=pd.`applyID` LEFT JOIN crm_client cc ON cc.client_ID=pa.client_ID WHERE 1=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and pd.delayBeginDate='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ORDER BY pd.delayBeginDate ASC
Reader.Description: SELECT cc.clientName, pp.projectName, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pp.bankName, CASE WHEN pd.delayBeginDate IS NULL THEN pp.delayBeginDate ELSE pd.delayBeginDate END delayBeginDate, pd.delayEndDate, -- pp.amanName, -- pp.bmanName, pp.beforeAManName, pp.beforeBManName, pa.fundSource, pp.subBankName, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pd.delaySum, pa.guarantyOrgName, pa.hostAreaName, pa.oprationCompanyName, pa.attributionName, pa.`guarantyOrgName`, pad.dcontractCode, cc.relationMainName, pp.loadCode FROM pro_delay pd LEFT JOIN pro_applyDetail pad ON pad.`apply_ID`=pd.applyID LEFT JOIN pro_project pp ON pd.project_ID=pp.`project_ID` LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.`apply_ID`=pd.`applyID` LEFT JOIN crm_client cc ON cc.client_ID=pa.client_ID WHERE 1=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and pd.delayBeginDate='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ORDER BY pd.delayBeginDate ASC

Reader.Name: tab_pay
Reader.Sql: SELECT pp.projectName, cc.clientName, pfp.paySum, pa.`guarantyOrgName`, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pp.delayBeginDate, pp.delayEndDate, pa.fundSource, pp.bankName, pfp.payDate, -- pp.amanName, -- pp.bmanName, pp.beforeAManName, pp.beforeBManName, pp.subBankName, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pa.guarantyOrgName, pa.hostAreaName, pa.oprationCompanyName, pa.attributionName, pad.dcontractCode, cc.relationMainName FROM pro_factPay pfp LEFT JOIN pro_applyDetail pad ON pad.`apply_ID`=pfp.applyID LEFT JOIN pro_project pp ON pfp.applyID=pp.`apply_ID` LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.`apply_ID`=pfp.`applyID` LEFT JOIN crm_client cc ON cc.client_ID = pa.client_ID WHERE 1=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and pfp.payDate='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ORDER BY pfp.payDate ASC
Reader.Description: SELECT pp.projectName, cc.clientName, pfp.paySum, pa.`guarantyOrgName`, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pp.delayBeginDate, pp.delayEndDate, pa.fundSource, pp.bankName, pfp.payDate, -- pp.amanName, -- pp.bmanName, pp.beforeAManName, pp.beforeBManName, pp.subBankName, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pa.guarantyOrgName, pa.hostAreaName, pa.oprationCompanyName, pa.attributionName, pad.dcontractCode, cc.relationMainName FROM pro_factPay pfp LEFT JOIN pro_applyDetail pad ON pad.`apply_ID`=pfp.applyID LEFT JOIN pro_project pp ON pfp.applyID=pp.`apply_ID` LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.`apply_ID`=pfp.`applyID` LEFT JOIN crm_client cc ON cc.client_ID = pa.client_ID WHERE 1=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and pfp.payDate='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ORDER BY pfp.payDate ASC

Reader.Name: tab_creditor
Reader.Sql: SELECT pc.creditor_sum, pp.projectName, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pp.loadBeginDate, pp.loadEndDate, pa.dContractCode, pp.loadCode FROM pro_creditor pc LEFT JOIN pro_project pp ON pp.project_ID=pc.project_id LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.apply_ID=pc.apply_id where 1=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and DATE_FORMAT(pc.creditor_date,'%Y-%m-%d')='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ${has(dataJurisdictionSql)?(dataJurisdictionSql):""}
Reader.Description: SELECT pc.creditor_sum, pp.projectName, CASE pp.busiClass WHEN "01" THEN "担保" WHEN "02" THEN "委贷" END busiClass, pa.fundChinese, pa.fundName, pp.loadBeginDate, pp.loadEndDate, pa.dContractCode, pp.loadCode FROM pro_creditor pc LEFT JOIN pro_project pp ON pp.project_ID=pc.project_id LEFT JOIN pro_apply pa ON pa.apply_ID=pc.apply_id where 1=1 ${has(enddatesql)?(" and DATE_FORMAT(pc.creditor_date,'%Y-%m-%d')='"+enddatesql+"'"):""} ${has(wheresql)?(" and wheresql='"+wheresql+"'"):""} ${has(dataJurisdictionSql)?(dataJurisdictionSql):""}
